# The live config: created from config.example.json by setup_pi.sh (or the
# first web-UI save) and rewritten at runtime by the web UI, so it is
# deliberately untracked -- web edits must not dirty the repo on the Pi.
# Anchored to the root: tests/fixtures/config.json stays tracked.
/config.json

# Runtime artifacts written by the config web UI (server/app.py).
config.json.bak
config.json.*.tmp